data.description: Welcome to this beautiful ranch style home! Combined with a newly finished basement that includes an egress window, which makes this house right around 3,898 square feet. The main level of this house welcomes you with an open floor plan, accentuated by an abundance of natural light, cathedral ceiling and a stone gas fireplace. The kitchen boasts top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, soft close drawers/cabinets and ample storage space. The master suite offers coffered ceiling, a large garden tub in the bathroom and a generous walk-in closet in the bedroom. The fully finished basement is the perfect space to entertain in style with a beautiful stone wet bar. Nestled in a desirable location, don't miss the chance to call this house your home! Agent Owned.
